00:00:40.226 --> 00:00:44.126 A:middle
It's a great moment
to end off this day.

00:00:44.126 --> 00:00:46.506 A:middle
I know it's been long, many of
you have been waiting in lines

00:00:46.506 --> 00:00:47.746 A:middle
around the building to get

00:00:47.746 --> 00:00:50.446 A:middle
