-- you got your lunch,

00:00:55.706 --> 00:00:59.236 A:middle
then you had State of the Union,
and that was a great session.

00:00:59.436 --> 00:01:03.526 A:middle
And now we want to finish
the day by taking a moment

WEBVTT
