the Super Evil Megacorp
team includes 35 developers

00:48:15.896 --> 00:48:18.716 A:middle
from Riot Games, Lizard
Entertainment, Rock Star Games,

00:48:18.886 --> 00:48:21.496 A:middle
Gorilla Games, Playfish,
Supercell, and more.

