and I can just comment on the
things that you are seeing

00:49:13.416 --> 00:49:15.806 A:middle
in terms of the quality of
work that these guys have done.

00:49:15.806 --> 00:49:23.236 A:middle
So if we could roll the video.

00:49:23.236 --> 00:49:25.096 A:middle
This game has been three years

00:49:25.256 --> 00:49:28.246 A:middle
in the making by
this small team.

00:49:31.586 --> 00:49:34.946 A:middle
The creators are huge MOBA
fans, and their goal was

00:49:35.046 --> 00:49:37.946 A:middle
to create a MOBA game
that they, themselves,

00:49:37.946 --> 00:49:39.716 A:middle
would want to play
on a touch device.

